				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-giang/poem-UajoSeGVub6lnzC779a8Hg">Bạch Đằng giang - 白藤江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Ti%C3%AAn-Chi/Giang-Nam-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-3u56JNGYqCZv0lULk7I2Bg">Giang Nam khúc kỳ 1 - 江南曲其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Ti%C3%AAn-Chi/author-0kMgiZ_WqcHPNSQmRfJIpA">Đinh Tiên Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Thái tang tử - 採桑子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Quan-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-AEC6I0cqYu-k5cNGd4tJCw">Trung thu dạ Đại Quan viên tức cảnh - 中秋夜大觀園即景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-FnnTxBaON8h_Pp60oZXQBg">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/Xu%C3%A2n-mu%E1%BB%99n-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-mwYMO1tBmBB7LXFMhnPP3Q">Xuân muộn ngẫu thành thập nhị vận - 春悶偶成十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
